# Retail Channel Pre-Screen

## When to Use
Load this file when Channel = Retail / Consumer-Facing. Run all three checks before the weighted validation matrix. If any check fails, stop immediately — do not generate a rationale table, do not register to the database.

---

## Pre-Screen Checks

### Pre-Screen A — Form Factor
Competitor form factor must match exactly:
`Fan-only` | `Fan-light combo` | `Fan-light-nightlight` | `Inline` | `Multi-port`

Mismatch = **HARD PASS. Stop.** Output "HARD PASS — Visual/Commercial Mismatch (Form Factor)."

### Pre-Screen B — Lighting Configuration
Fan-only → Fan-only required. Combo → Combo required.
Any lighting addition or removal = **HARD PASS. Stop.**

Output "HARD PASS — Visual/Commercial Mismatch (Lighting Configuration)."
*(Lighting addition changes electrical rough-in = HIGH correction cost. Lighting removal = feature regression = guaranteed consumer complaint.)*

### Pre-Screen C — Grille Profile
Square → Square | Round → Round | Flush → Flush | Decorative → Decorative

Mismatch = **Best Option maximum. Cannot be TRUE.**
Document "Grille Mismatch" in Notes. Correction Cost Exposure = MEDIUM.
*(Pre-Screen C is not a hard stop — proceed to matrix with Best Option ceiling.)*

---

## Pre-Screen Output Block

Output this table before the rationale table on all retail channel runs:

| Pre-Screen | Requirement | Competitor | Canarm Match | Pass/Fail |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Form Factor | Identical category | X | Y | Pass/Fail |
| Lighting Config | Must match | X | Y | Pass/Fail |
| Grille Profile | Compatible shape/style | X | Y | Pass/Fail |

---

## Contractor Channel Notes
When Channel = Contractor, run Pre-Screen A, B, C as **documentation fields only** — not hard gates. Record results in the rationale table rows (Form Factor, Lighting Config, Grille Profile). Let contractor decide. Ensure mismatch decisions are recorded in Notes, not buried.

---

## Correction Cost Exposure — Pre-Screen Defaults

| Pre-Screen Failure | Default Exposure |
|---|---|
| Form Factor mismatch | CRITICAL |
| Lighting Config mismatch | HIGH (electrical change required) |
| Grille Profile mismatch | MEDIUM |
